import React from 'react'
import{
HeroContainer,
HeroBg,
HeroVideo
} from './HeroSectionElements'
import Video from '../../videos/video.mp4'


const HeroSection = () => {
    return (
        <HeroContainer id="home">
            <HeroBg> 
                <HeroVideo autoPlay loop muted src={Video} type="video/mp4"/>
            </HeroBg>
            <HeroContent>
                <HeroH1>Banco Virtual</HeroH1>
                <HeroP>Crea tu cuenta y reciviras $250.000 para tus primeras compras.</HeroP>
                <HeroBtnWrapper>
                    <Button></Button>
                </HeroBtnWrapper>
            </HeroContent>
        </HeroContainer>
    )
}

export default HeroSection;
